{"tid":919953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「女版東方神起」韓國32歲女歌手Dana 亮刀直播 嗆：「發不了唱片都是你們害的」","createTime":"2018-11-28T12:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T14:44:50.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4c02fe57e14e621070377eec17f4a74cd22b53e8","tid":919953,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:33:36.000Z","msg":"韓國32歲女歌手喜悅（Dana）以「女版東方神起」天上智喜出道，曾經走紅一時，但歷經團員解約、情變、爆肥、唱片銷售不佳後，事業跌到谷底，雖然近來重新振作，甚至上了減重節目誓言減肥，沒想到近日竟然在與粉絲直播時亮刀嗆聲說，自己發不了唱片都是歌迷害的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-28/656/20181128004188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-28%2F656%2F20181128004188.jpg&h=9ba0d4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓女團天上智喜出身的歌手Dana直播亮刀威脅粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n南韓元祖女團「天上智喜」由天舞（Stephanie）、上美（Lina）、智聲（Sunday）、喜悅（Dana）4位成員組成，曾經紅極一時，被稱為「螞蟻腰王后」，但當中持續在演藝圈的成員Dana，近來再曝光卻爆肥走樣。<br />\n<br />\n「女版東方神起」大爆肥 元祖女偶像走鐘嚇壞粉絲<br />\n<br />\n日前在與歌迷直播時，有歌迷問她何時回歸，她理智線斷掉回嗆：「那也要音源成績好才能出啊！」她直言過去推出的《Touch You》歌曲反應不好，「你們那時候幫我音源刷到1位的話，我還可以推出solo的。」當場嗆聲歌迷「不是音源榜的錯，是你們的錯！」她在直播期間數度亮刀以及中指。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBQ8XoO.img?h=450&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=397&amp;y=322\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBQ8XoO.img%3Fh%3D450%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D397%26y%3D322&h=e9787938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣失控的行為，讓歌迷當場傻眼，雖然有死忠歌迷為她緩頰可能是減肥心情不好，但網路撻伐四起，所屬經紀公司SM娛樂代表她發出道歉聲明，上午6時天文台錄得氣溫19度，相對濕度百分之96。「為我個人在IG上做出的錯誤行為以及過度的舉止道歉，很抱歉造成大家傷害，我會深深反省，全都是我惹的禍。」"},{"pid":"f142340e2c75b86d2b2c7b3efe37458a416bf21e","tid":919953,"uid":49391,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63W7osp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63W7osp.gif&h=d9eb6712&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5a2f5b7b91900e09e00a53aa57f7863ae1e02b0","tid":919953,"uid":143288,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">所屬經紀公司SM娛樂代表她發出道歉聲明，上午6時天文台錄得氣溫19度，相對濕度百分之96。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主真係好有趣"},{"pid":"6bd7aa3a595c49522ad505d412d07a0ddf569479","tid":919953,"uid":7050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"細個都幾可愛 依家痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f8effd7fb3ed6d5fc6b8e56521ae5ab3fe1eaa","tid":919953,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"點解把刀要打格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752f625aa4e2ef826a064b78a52af37a4745cb11","tid":919953,"uid":171594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"係咪俾人潛完規則先暴肥<br />\n仲搞到癲癲地"},{"pid":"e904260b6d733c9e731b02bb9aa36a2658bc695a","tid":919953,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5a2f5b7b91900e09e00a53aa57f7863ae1e02b0","tid":919953,"uid":143288,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">所屬經紀公司SM娛樂代表她發出道歉聲明，上午6時天文台錄得氣溫19度，相對濕度百分之96。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主真係好有趣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"特色嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7feea07039d63b4aace84ebcbb57f17f3476c40","tid":919953,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a2f5b7b91900e09e00a53aa57f7863ae1e02b0","tid":919953,"uid":143288,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:56:29.000Z","ms